.------------------------------------------------------
. Variables required for Standard Graph Screen
.------------------------------------------------------
          INC       SCRGPHFD/INC
.------------------------------------------------------
. To create a Graph Display.
.
.  1. Create Temp File
.
.      PACK      FILENAME,GPHTMPNM,PORT
.      REP       " 0",FILENAME
.      PACK      COMMAND,GPHISBU,FILENAME,GPHTMPID
.      EXECUTE   COMMAND,TASKID
.
.  2. Fill Temp File with Information to be Graphed
.
.  3. Setup Parameters.
.      GPHBLKX   FORM      1         * Block Width X/Y
.      GPHBLKY   FORM      1         * Block Width Y/X
.      GPHTYPE   FORM      1         * Graph Type 0=X/Y, 1=Y/X
.      GPHNOCO   FORM      2         * Number of Columns per Period  
.      GPHNTYP   FORM      1         * Number of Types Displayed
.      GPHNAME   DIM       80        * Graph Name
.      GPHLEDG   DIM       15[10]    * Ledgend Descriptions
.
.------------------------------------------------------
GPHTMPNM  INIT      "scrgph"  * Tempory file name for Graph Display
GPHISBU   INIT      "isbuild "
GPHTMPID  INIT      " 108 U1-3,4-6 U1-3,7-27,4-6"
GPHCOMM   DIM       80
GPHFNAME  DIM       8
.
GPHBLKX   FORM      1         * Block Width X/Y
GPHBLKY   FORM      1         * Block Width Y/X
GPHBCNT   FORM      1         * Block Width Counter
GPHTYPE   FORM      1         * Graph Type 0=X/Y, 1=Y/X
GPHNOCOX  FORM      2         * Number of Columns per Period
GPHNOCOY  FORM      2         * Period Description Width      Y type
GPHNTYP   FORM      1         * Number of Types Displayed
GPHNAME   DIM       80        * Graph Name
GPHLEDG   DIM       15[9]     * Ledgend Descriptions
.
GPHDTYP   FORM      1         * Current Display Type
GPHCURR   DIM       6         * Current Items to Display
GPHNEXT   DIM       6         * Next Items to Display
GPHSPER   DIM       3         * Save Period
GPHOFSET  FORM      12        * Offset
AXIS      FORM      2         * Calculated Axis Position
DSCALE    FORM      21        * Display Scale Amounts
SCALE     FORM      21        * Calculated Scale
GRAPHMAX  FORM      12.8      * Maximum
MAXIMUM   FORM      12.8      * Maximum
MINIMUM   FORM      12.8      * Minimum
GVALUE    FORM      12.8      * Value
F12P4     FORM      12.4      * Calculation Variable
F12P8     FORM      12.8      * Calculation Variable
F12       FORM      12        * CalCulated Position
GPHTMPF2  FORM      2         * Temp Calculation Variable
GPHSP70   INIT      "                                   ":
                    "                                   "
GRAPHMSG  DIM       80
GRAPHD24  DIM       80
GRAPHA24  DIM       80
.
